    "text": "Benedict Cumberbatch scene one take one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.303,
    "endTime": 6.106,
    "text": "When did I know I wanted to be an actor?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.106,
    "endTime": 8.719999999999999,
    "text": "When did Shakespeare know that he wanted to write?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.82,
    "endTime": 11.545,
    "text": "When did Starbucks make his first Frappuccino?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.619,
    "endTime": 19.62,
    "text": "That one got me Dr. Strange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.921,
    "endTime": 23.256,
    "text": "A true actor only wants to act."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.124,
    "endTime": 27.06,
    "text": "And the reality is I don't know how to do anything else."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.06,
