    "text": "It's... the other side..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.8,
    "endTime": 32.799,
    "text": "Where are the instructions?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.902,
    "endTime": 37.104,
    "text": "Great acting requires training."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.104,
    "endTime": 40.03,
    "text": "You have to train hard to act great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.03,
    "endTime": 42.943,
    "text": "Are we going to do anything besides watch episodes of Sherlock?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.943,
    "endTime": 45.12,
    "text": "Now you made me miss my favorite part so I have to rewind it to the beginning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.72,
    "endTime": 47.347,
    "text": "You need to learn from the master."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.5,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "It won't be easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Try the line."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.618,
    "endTime": 52.7,
    "text": "Where's my mother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.7,
    "endTime": 52.853,
    "text": "Again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.853,
    "endTime": 54.288000000000004,
    "text": "Where is my mother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.988,
    "endTime": 54.5,
    "text": "Where is your mother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 55.788,
    "text": "Where is my mother?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.789,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "WHERE IS YOUR MOTHER?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
