  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 65.799,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.799,
    "endTime": 68.936,
    "text": "If you want to succeed, you have to really want it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.936,
    "endTime": 72.572,
    "text": "And for that to work, your art must be your passion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.572,
    "endTime": 73.84,
    "text": "The doctor said it's for sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.84,
    "endTime": 75.108,
    "text": "The test came in positive."
