  {
    "startTime": 160.994,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.764,
    "text": "Do it for the right reasons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.764,
    "endTime": 166.767,
    "text": "The only reason to become an actor is to become famous and rich."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.767,
    "endTime": 170.537,
    "text": "And if you succeed you will touch people metaphorically."
